' Notebook Shared with you
= "\r\n" * 2
' #{@owner.name}
- if !@owner.org.blank?
  '  (#{@owner.org})
' has shared with you the notebook #{@notebook.title}: #{@url + notebook_path(@notebook)}
-unless @message.blank?
  = "\r\n"
  ' message: #{@message}
' Please visit the #{GalleryConfig.site.name} today to create your account: #{@url}
